      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "that when I am put out of the stewardship; drove from Jerusalem, and from the temple and the synagogues: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "they may receive me into their houses; either Jews or Gentiles, after their dispersion. ",
        "children": [
